    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扩展你的吸血鬼巢穴</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/1d78296f72bd5718698237b6fb38a108.poster.avif?t=1758287212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/1d78296f72bd5718698237b6fb38a108.webm?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/1d78296f72bd5718698237b6fb38a108.mp4?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过解锁新的房间和楼层来建造和扩建您的城堡。每一次扩展都会提供新的机会来增强吸血鬼的能力，并解锁更多游戏功能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>释放血魔法 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/f7b98fe95bfaedb6bcbf6237738a7d12.poster.avif?t=1758287212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/f7b98fe95bfaedb6bcbf6237738a7d12.webm?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/f7b98fe95bfaedb6bcbf6237738a7d12.mp4?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名吸血鬼，挥舞血魔法与人类和怪物作战。从敌人身上吸血可以增强吸血鬼的敏捷性--时滞。这项独特的技能能让你在敌人心中播下绝望的种子--使用它能让你的敌人僵在原地，而你和你的吸血鬼同伴则以难以想象的速度实施攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>控制多个吸血鬼</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/8177b94675ba32cc96db6f2dfbbbe525.poster.avif?t=1758287212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/8177b94675ba32cc96db6f2dfbbbe525.webm?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/8177b94675ba32cc96db6f2dfbbbe525.mp4?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吸血鬼家族》中的狩猎变得更具战略性，因为您最多可同时控制三个吸血鬼，每个吸血鬼都有自己独特的技能。在投入战斗之前，您将决定吸血鬼的最佳战术和专长。玩家可以在吸血鬼之间随意切换，向其他吸血鬼发出指令。时空停滞系统让管理多个吸血鬼变得更加直观，让你可以放慢时间，精确计划你的攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隐身还是战斗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/0aa5a0ae5393312699c7eddd4b999f84.poster.avif?t=1758287212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/0aa5a0ae5393312699c7eddd4b999f84.webm?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/0aa5a0ae5393312699c7eddd4b999f84.mp4?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并非每场战斗都需要正面交锋。阴影是你最大的盟友。利用隐身术和训练有素的蝙蝠跟踪猎物，或逐一消灭群体中的敌人。巧妙地躲避侦查可以让你在不直接交战的情况下消灭对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复杂的部族政治</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/677578e7373a6642e85aa35aad44ed92.poster.avif?t=1758287212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/677578e7373a6642e85aa35aad44ed92.webm?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/677578e7373a6642e85aa35aad44ed92.mp4?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《吸血鬼家族》的世界中，充满了敌对吸血鬼家族之间的政治阴谋。这些派系为争夺权力而战，互相袭击对方的前哨站，并在街头发生冲突。政治系统允许您结成联盟或敌对势力，这将影响您的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为巴黎瘟疫</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/324aff7d97c5ddd165b34068b5539392.poster.avif?t=1758287212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/324aff7d97c5ddd165b34068b5539392.webm?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578940/extras/324aff7d97c5ddd165b34068b5539392.mp4?t=1758287212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入一个广阔的非线性世界，这里是 19 世纪巴黎的缩影。地图按区域划分，在指引您探索的同时，还标明了敌人的难度。随着您向城市深处探索，敌人会变得更具挑战性，您需要强化自己的角色才能生存下来。这种开放世界的设计为您带来了丰富的 RPG 体验，在这里，探索既是一种奖励，也是一种危险。</p>",
